Mediocre potato shaped like a nerd, sometimes makes art with his disgusting yet peculiar potato arms.

summary: " I have always been really picky about the films that I make, because I think that there’s such an incredible opportunity to...
body: “ I have always been really picky about the films that I make, because I think that there’s such an incredible opportunity to bring up questions when you’re making movies, and some of my favorite films bring up big questions. They are movies that, when you walk away from it, it hits you as something deeper, and it’s a great, fun way to be able to bounce around some of these harder concepts in our heads.”
